Description
nl.codevs.strinput.examples.discord
Discord bot implementation using this commands system.
Main classes to pay attention to: DiscordBot An example of an implemented bot class with the command system. DiscordCenter The command center which is attached to the main class of a plugin. DiscordUser A user implementation with functions to send messages and derivatives to a Discord user. nl.codevs.strinput.examples.discord.extensions Extensions to the parameter parsing and context handling
nl.codevs.strinput.examples.discord.extensions
Discord command system parameter and context extensions.
nl.codevs.strinput.examples.spigotmc
Spigot plugin implementation using this commands system.
Main classes to pay attention to: SpigotPlugin An example of an implemented plugin class with the command system. SpigotCenter The command center which is attached to the main class of a plugin. SpigotUser A user implementation with functions to send messages and derivatives to a player. nl.codevs.strinput.examples.spigotmc.extensions Extensions to the parameter parsing and context handling
nl.codevs.strinput.examples.spigotmc.extensions
Extensions to parameter and context handler lists.
nl.codevs.strinput.system
StrInput system implementation.
nl.codevs.strinput.system.context
Built-in context handlers and the context handler interface: StrContextHandler
All extra context handlers must implement this interface.
nl.codevs.strinput.system.parameter
Parameter handlers for types.
Each parameter handler must extend StrParameterHandler and will handle a select set of types.
nl.codevs.strinput.system.text
Contains colors (C) and an abstract text implementation (Str).
nl.codevs.strinput.system.util
Utility classes.
nl.codevs.strinput.system.virtual
Contains virtual representations and handlers of categories (StrVirtualCategory), commands (StrVirtualCommand), and parameters (StrVirtualParameter).
Including an interface (StrVirtual) for shared functions.
